{"tid":1931614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2022年睇世界杯定奧運","createTime":"2020-03-18T09:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T09:42:58.000Z","uid":148002,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d61baa226ff142b6f1e4c0ac152554f32029b768","tid":1931614,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />世界杯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奧運<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，因應武漢肺炎在全球大流行，致全球體壇全面停擺，東京奧組委理事高橋治，主張將東京奧運延期2年，在<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2022年夏天才舉辦，更獲得不少委員支持，據報本月30日東京奧組委將會開會討論，照目前情況東京奧運延期機會頗高。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n高橋治認為，以目前的形勢最好將東京奧運延遲一或兩年，不過認為由於明年7月日本福岡會舉行世界游泳錦標賽，明年8月又有世界田徑錦標賽，故最好延遲到2022年夏天舉行。雖然2022年該年同樣會有在北京舉行的冬季奧運會及卡塔爾世界盃，但兩項賽事都不會在夏天舉行，故認為延期兩年舉行的效果最好，獲得不少理事支持。<br />\n同時東京奧組委與國際奧委會，同樣堅決企硬不會閉門作賽，認為會令全球觀眾失去興趣。東京奧組委又認為，要等疫情完全消失，以最安全的方式舉行奧運，故延期兩年是最安全的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過報道指出，東京奧運能否順利舉辦，最終決定權還是國際奧委會，不過東京奧組委的意見，對東奧是否延期甚至取消是相當重要。"},{"pid":"9433ac5dc5dcb09ea83c99af0cc68da203050b6d","tid":1931614,"uid":148002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"唔知到時仲有冇牙朗，小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd14da8f05083ad7e8d9921b0a8525c7cff9bea","tid":1931614,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdabc649e1423f7721693b5dc1ec3150030d5cb","tid":1931614,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"8bb6ccc49bbfeee7aa438b21bf4013c61d60d676","tid":1931614,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcdabc649e1423f7721693b5dc1ec3150030d5cb","tid":1931614,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b185af9a91389935bf66d8cd87ba9d91248d85b3","tid":1931614,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"爭咩鳩呀<br />\n垃圾fifa 奶卡塔爾袋底<br />\n改咗冬天搞世界盃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}